title: New Balance Women's 515 V3 Sneaker
description: Created for both comfort and style, the New Balance WL515V3 is poised to become your next everyday staple. Featuring classic logo branding and an '80s-inspired upper, these women's casual shoes keep your look above the trends. These kicks also include a lightweight EVA midsole and comfort insert for underfoot cushioning that helps you get through your day with ease.
